{"word":"G2048 - ἔρημος - érēmos - er'-ay-mos - Desert","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔρημος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">érēmos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er'-ay-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Desert</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாழான, அநாதையான, வனாந்தரமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. solitary, lonely, desolate, uninhabited"},{"paragraph":"2. a desert, wilderness"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain affinity; <i>lonesome</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>waste</i> (usually as a noun, <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a> being implied): - desert, desolate, solitary, wilderness.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2047/2047\">G2047</a>, <a href=\"#/G2048/2048\">G2048</a>, <a href=\"#/G2049/2049\">G2049</a>, <a href=\"#/G2050/2050\">G2050</a>"}]}